es%20%26quot%3BBrutally%20Murdered%26quot%3B%20Shortly%20Before%20We%20Reached%20Them%3A%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20announced%20today%20that%20it%20had%20discovered%20the%20bodies%20of%20six%20hostages%20in%20an%20underground%20tunnel%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Among%20the%20dead%20were%20dual%20citizens%2C%20including%20a%20US-Israeli%20and%20a%20Russian-Israeli.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20claimed%20that%20the%20hostages%20were%20brutally%20murdered%20by%20Hamas%20shortly%20before%20security%20forces%20could%20reach%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%2C%20whose%20identities%20have%20been%20confirmed%20as%20Carmel%20Gat%2C%20Eden%20Yerushalmi%2C%20Hersh%20Goldberg-Polin%2C%20Alexander%20Lobanov%2C%20Almog%20Sarusi%2C%20and%20Ori%20Danino%2C%20were%20kidnapped%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20their%20brutal%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20The%20attack%20not%20only%20triggered%20the%20ongoing%20war%20but%20also%20led%20to%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20251%20individuals%2C%20of%20whom%2097%20remain%20captive%2C%20including%2033%20who%20the%20Israeli%20army%20believes%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20hours%20ago%2C%20we%20informed%20the%20families%20that%20the%20bodies%20of%20their%20loved%20ones%20had%20been%20located%20by%20IDF%20troops%20in%20an%20underground%20tunnel%20in%20Rafah.%20According%20to%20our%20initial%20assessment%2C%20they%20were%20brutally%20murdered%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20shortly%20before%20we%20reached%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20spokesperson%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20difficult%20morning%20here%20in%20Israel.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCarmel%2C%20Ori%2C%20Eden%2C%20Almog%2C%20Alex%2C%20Hersh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMurdered%20in%20cold%20blood%20by%20Hamas%20while%20in%20captivity.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMay%20their%20memory%20be%20a%20blessing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOAdZg8ZxB2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOAdZg8ZxB2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C%20(%40Israel)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%2Fstatus%2F1830114580992844271%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%20were%20reportedly%20taken%20alive%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20their%20bodies%20were%20discovered%20during%20combat%20operations%20in%20Rafah%2C%20approximately%20one%20kilometre%20from%20a%20tunnel%20where%20another%20hostage%2C%20Farhan%20Alkadi%2C%20had%20been%20rescued%20just%20days%20earlier.%20Hagari%20claimed%20that%20the%20IDF%20had%20been%20operating%20under%20extreme%20caution%2C%20knowing%20that%20additional%20hostages%20might%20be%20held%20in%20the%20area.%20However%2C%20they%20lacked%20precise%20information%20on%20the%20hostages'%20exact%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20of%20the%20bodies%20came%20amidst%20ongoing%20combat%20in%20Rafah%2C%20where%20IDF%20troops%20continued%20to%20engage%20with%20Hamas%20fighters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%2C%20our%20hearts%20are%20broken%20alongside%20the%20families%20of%20Ori%20Danino%2C%20Alex%20Lobanov%2C%20Almog%20Sarusi%2C%20Hersh%20Goldberg-Polin%2C%20Carmel%20Gat%2C%20and%20Eden%20Yerushalmi%2C%26quot%3B%20Hagari%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20put%20into%20words%20what%20the%20hostages%20have%20endured%20in%20Hamas%20captivity%20since%20October%207th%2C%20now%20331%20days%2C%20and%20what%20their%20families%20have%20been%20going%20through.%20This%20morning%2C%20this%20news%20shakes%20us%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20six%20victims%2C%20Gat%20was%20abducted%20from%20the%20southern%20Israeli%20kibbutz%20community%20of%20Beeri%20and%20the%20others%2C%20aged%20between%2023