rump-t-shirt%2Famp_articleshow%2F112962559.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhawk-tuah-spit-on-that-thang-man-kicked-out-of-delta-flight-over-trump-t-shirt%2Famp_articleshow%2F112962559.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA's%20%26quot%3BHit%20With%20Footwear%26quot%3B%20Protest%20In%20Mumbai%20Over%20Shivaji%20Statue%20Collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Nana%20Patole%20--%20have%20joined%20the%20mega%20%26quot%3BJode%20Maro%26quot%3B%20protest%20in%20Mumbai%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20Chhattrapati%20Shivaji's%2035-foot%20statue%20at%20Malvan%20in%20Sindhudurg.%20Massive%20security%20has%20been%20deployed%20by%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20for%20the%20protest%20march%20from%C2%A0Hutatma%20Chowk%20in%20the%20Fort%20area%20to%20Gateway%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20posse%20of%20police%20personnel%20of%20security%20forces%20has%20gathered%20at%20the%20Gateway%20of%20India.%20The%20monument%20has%20also%20been%20shut%20for%20tourists%2C%20citing%20law%20and%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20questioned%20the%20relevance%20of%20the%20protest%20and%20has%20planned%20a%20march%20of%20its%20own%20to%20counter%20the%20Opposition's%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20bloc%20has%20called%20its%20agitation%20%26quot%3Bjode%20maro%26quot%3B%20protest%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bhit%20with%20footwear%26quot%3B.%20Calling%20upon%20people%20to%20join%20the%20march%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20tweeted%20that%20it%20is%20coming%20to%20bow%20at%20Shivaji's%20feet%20to%20%26quot%3Bawaken%20the%20pride%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B.%20The%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20NCP%20has%20said%20there%20is%20no%20forgiveness%20for%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20Shivdrohis%26quot%3B.%20The%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20the%20march%20is%20aimed%20at%20teaching%20a%20lesson%20to%20%26quot%3BShivdrohis%26quot%3B%20who%20did%20shoddy%20work%2C%20committed%20corruption%20and%20insulted%20Shivaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20the%20Shivaji%20statue%2C%20which%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20just%208%20months%20back%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20project%20was%20handled%20by%20the%20Navy%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20state%20government.%20Police%20have%20arrested%20the%20structural%20consultant%20for%20the%20project%20and%20its%20contractor.%20They%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20act%20endangering%20life%20and%20safety%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20political%20backlash%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20apologised%20to%20the%20people%20for%20the%20statue's%20collapse.%20%26quot%3BChhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20is%20not%20just%20a%20name%20or%20a%20king.%20For%20us%2C%20he%20is%20our%20deity.%20Today%2C%20I%20bow%20my%20head%20at%20his%20feet%20and%20apologise%20to%20my%20deity.%20I%20also%20apologise%20to%20the%20people%20hurt%20by%20the%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Questions%20INDIA%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20has%20said%20the%20Opposition%20is%20politicising%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BFor%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP%20are%20insulting%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20never%20spoke%20a%20word%20about%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20from%20Red%20Fort%2C%20will%20the%20Congress%20apologise%3F%20PM%20Modi%20has%20apologised%2C%20but%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20leaders%20are%20politicising%20the%20issue%20because%20the%20polls%20are%20approaching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20state%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Keshav%20Upadhye%20said%20the%20Opposition's%20love%20for%20Shivaji%20is%20superficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20PM's%20apology%20not%20enough%3F%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20apologised%20for%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20Rafale%20episode.%20Will%20they%20(MVA)%20stage%20a%20similar%20protest%20for%20these%20apologies%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Upadhye%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20party's%20youth%20wing%20would%20stage%20agitations%20near%20statues%20of%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20across%20Maharashtra%20to%20%26quot%3Bexpose%26quot%3B%20the%20Opposition.%20He%20alleged%20that%20previous%20Congress-led%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20did%20nothing%20to%20preserve%20the%20forts%20of%20Shivaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20holding%20an%20agitation%20in%20Dadar%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20city%20party%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20to%20counter%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725171360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbvf2m4l8_shivaji-statue_625x300_01_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivaji-statue-collapse-protest-vs-protest-in-mumbai-as-india-raises-pitch-6464103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20deployed%20heavy%20security%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20Mumbai%20protest%20announced%20by%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20over%20the%20collapse%20of%20Chhattrapati%20Shivaji's%2035-foot%20statue%20at%20Malvan%20in%20Sindhudurg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivaji-statue-collapse-protest-vs-protest-in-mumbai-as-india-raises-pitch-6464103%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'There%20are%2010%20other%20players%20in%20the%20team'%3A%20Teammate%20defends%20Babar%20Azam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17251711110