ve%20friends%20who%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20create%20nudes%20of%20their%20peers%2C%20a%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFaced%20with%20online%20sexual%20encounters%2C%20kids%20prefer%20social%20media%20reporting%20over%20talking%20to%20adults.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20problematic%20enough%20that%20some%20kids%20are%20sending%20nude%20photos%20of%20themselves%20to%20friends%20and%20even%20online%20strangers.%20But%20artificial%20intelligence%20has%20elevated%20the%20problem%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%201%20in%2010%20children%20say%20their%20friends%20or%20peers%20have%20used%20generative%20AI%20to%20create%20nudes%20of%20other%20kids%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20Thorn.%20The%20nonprofit%2C%20which%20fights%20child%20sex%20abuse%2C%20surveyed%20over%201%2C000%20children%20ages%209%20to%2017%20in%20late%202023%20for%20its%20annual%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThorn%20found%20that%2012%25%20of%20children%20ages%209%20to%2012%20knew%20of%20friends%20or%20classmates%20who%20had%20used%20AI%20to%20create%20nudes%20of%20their%20peers%2C%20and%208%25%20preferred%20not%20to%20answer%20the%20question.%20For%2013%20to%2017-year-olds%20surveyed%2C%2010%25%20said%20they%20knew%20of%20peers%20who%20had%20used%20AI%20to%20generate%20nudes%20of%20other%20kids%2C%20and%2011%25%20preferred%20not%20to%20answer.%20This%20was%20Thorn's%20first%20survey%20that%20asked%20children%20about%20the%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20to%20create%20deepfake%20nudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20motivation%20behind%20these%20events%20is%20more%20likely%20driven%20by%20adolescents%20acting%20out%20than%20an%20intent%20to%20sexually%20abuse%2C%20the%20resulting%20harms%20to%20victims%20are%20real%20and%20should%20not%20be%20minimized%20in%20attempts%20to%20wave%20off%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Thorn%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESexting%20culture%20is%20hard%20enough%20to%20tackle%20without%20AI%20being%20added%20to%20the%20mix.%20Thorn%20found%20that%2025%25%20of%20minors%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20to%20share%20nudes%20of%20themselves%20(a%20slight%20decrease%20from%20surveys%20dating%20back%20to%202019)%2C%20and%2013%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20reported%20having%20done%20so%20already%20at%20some%20point%2C%20a%20slight%20decline%20from%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nonprofit%20says%20sharing%20nude%20photos%20can%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsextortion-snapchat-teens-nudes-extortion-online-bullying-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esextortion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20bad%20actors%20using%20nude%20photos%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-lawsuit-snapchat-google-apple-exploited-marine-california-child-abuse-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblackmail%20or%20exploit%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20sender.%20Those%20who%20had%20considered%20sharing%20nudes%20identified%20leaks%20or%20exploitation%20as%20a%20reason%20that%20they%20ultimately%20chose%20not%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20Thorn%20asked%20young%20people%20about%20being%20paid%20for%20sending%20naked%20pictures%2C%20and%2013%25%20of%20kids%20surveyed%20said%20they%20knew%20of%20a%20friend%20who%20had%20been%20compensated%20for%20their%20nudes%2C%20while%207%25%20did%20not%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22937bcb90-1f5b-4fef-98d3-045ca06a0506%5C%22%3EKids%20want%20social%20media%20companies%20to%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20allows%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20realistic%20abuse%20imagery%20from%20benign%20sources%20such%20as%20school%20photos%20and%20social%20media%20posts%2C%26quot%3B%20Thorn's%20report%20said.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20victims%20who%20may%20have%20previously%20reported%20an%20incident%20to%20authorities%20can%20easily%20be%20revictimized%20with%20customized%2C%20new%20abusive%20material.%20For%20example%2C%20actor