0to%20a%20paper%20mill%20or%20moulded%20product%20unit%20to%20close%20the%20loop%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Seetharaman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20piece%20of%20waste%2C%20be%20it%20plastic%20or%20paper%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20sent%20to%20the%20landfills%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20BG%20Seetharaman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725026390000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D363572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indic%20Initiatives%2C%20the%20brainchild%20of%20B%20G%20Seetharaman%2C%20Vinay%20Kumar%20and%20Rajeeva%20Deekshit%20has%20pioneered%20an%20end-to-end%20machine%20that%20recycles%20difficult-to-process%20paper%20waste%20like%20paper%20cups%2C%20tetra%20pak%2C%20and%20tissues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20is%20the%20plan%20to%20give%20polio%20vaccines%20to%20children%20in%20Gaza%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725024890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa853%2Flive%2F20323ca0-66e2-11ef-b970-9f202720b57a.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4gejxxk820o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pauses%20to%20fighting%20will%20allow%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Gaza%20children%20to%20be%20vaccinated%20against%20polio.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com