0textiles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20prides%20their%20silk%20production%20techniques%20on%20being%20cruelty-free.%20%E2%80%9COur%20focus%20is%20on%20Ahimsa%20silk%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98eri%E2%80%99%20silk%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meynell%20explains.%20The%20name%20borrows%20from%20the%20Assamese%20word%20%E2%80%98era%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20castor.%20In%20contrast%20to%20mulberry%20silk%2C%20which%20is%20spun%20using%20long%20continuous%20fibres%20and%20involves%20boiling%20of%20the%20cocoons%20(thus%20killing%20the%20silkworms)%2C%20eri%20silk%20production%20is%20a%20less%20harmful%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%2C%20the%20cocoons%20are%20boiled%20once%20the%20silkworms%20complete%20their%20metamorphosis%20into%20butterflies%20and%20moths.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20way%2C%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20disturbing%20their%20life%20cycle%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meynell%20points%20out.%20The%20weaving%20studio%20has%20also%20given%20an%20impetus%20to%20the%20artisans%20in%20the%20area%20who%20earn%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F253969%2Freshamandi-agri-tech-startup-silk-farmers-karnataka-mayank-tiwari-utkarsh-apoorv-nift-sericulture-mulberry-iot-ai-business-technology-agriculture-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilk%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20turning%20the%20silk%20into%20textiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPractising%20what%20they%20preach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeka%20and%20Meynell%20shy%20away%20from%20making%20bold%20statements%20about%20their%20sustainable%20endeavours.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20it%20more%20as%20a%20set%20of%20lifestyle%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deka%20notes.%20Instead%20of%20positioning%20Medini%20Homestay%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98idyllic%20sustainable%20spot%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20dare%20to%20contradict%20conventional%20approaches%E2%80%99%2C%20Deka%20says%20it%20is%20instead%